CHOI BAEK-HO

17
00:01:46,523 --> 00:01:49,734
Come on. Again?

18
00:01:49,818 --> 00:01:51,694
Why would she ruin the vibe?

19
00:01:51,778 --> 00:01:54,948
Wasn't my song better
for celebrating her graduation?

20
00:01:57,784 --> 00:01:59,828
-On--
-On a rainy day

21
