Just say you don't.
He'll keep bothering you.

862
01:01:46,703 --> 01:01:47,995
When can I begin?

863
01:01:49,330 --> 01:01:50,248
Right now!

864
01:01:51,124 --> 01:01:54,168
Perfect. All right. Here I go.

865
01:01:54,252 --> 01:01:55,128
Okay.

866
01:01:55,962 --> 01:01:56,963
I can, right?

